parameters.name: AsyncId
parameters.description: The ID of the asynchronous task.

parameters.name: ClusterId
parameters.description: The ID of the E-HPC cluster. You can call the [ListClusters](~~87116~~) operation to query the cluster ID.

parameters.name: PageNumber
parameters.description:
The page number.\
Pages start from page 1.\
Default value: 1.

parameters.name: PageSize
parameters.description:
The number of entries returned per page.\
Valid values: 1 to 50.\
Default value: 10.
